  "description": "Oscar's external gills as a sound. Breathy, fluttering tremolo from LFO2 modulating the spectral tilt — the sound pulses between dark and bright like gill fronds waving in current. Low effort whisper territory with warm baritone vowels. A rhythmic, organic texture that invites you to slow down and breathe with it.",
